WEBVTT

00:00:00.533 --> 00:00:02.969
The goal of the Department's performance appraisal system is

00:00:03.036 --> 00:00:06.906
to assist the Department and Bargaining Unit Employees in

00:00:06.973 --> 00:00:10.243
maximizing their contribution to the Department's mission and the

00:00:10.310 --> 00:00:12.679
Employees' work goals.

00:00:12.746 --> 00:00:17.250
To that end, the system is used to: identify and communicate

00:00:17.317 --> 00:00:21.354
work goals for Employees and teams, identify and address

00:00:21.421 --> 00:00:25.325
Employee developmental needs, assess and improve Employee

00:00:25.392 --> 00:00:30.029
performance, recognize and reward Employee accomplishments,

00:00:30.096 --> 00:00:34.968
and base appropriate personnel actions on performance appraisal results.

00:00:35.034 --> 00:00:38.037
Article 22 covers the Department's responsibilities

00:00:38.104 --> 00:00:41.674
and timelines for managing performance appraisals.


